This BEVOID Software License Agreement ("Agreement" or "License") is a legally
binding contract between you ("Licensee", "you", or "your") and the BEVoid
Project ("Licensor", "we", "us", or "our") regarding your use of the BEVoid
software project, including all source code, object code, documentation,
assets, trademarks, and related intellectual property (collectively, the
"Software" or "BEVoid").

By accessing, downloading, installing, copying, modifying, distributing, or
otherwise using the Software, you acknowledge that you have read, understood,
and agree to be bound by the terms and conditions of this Agreement. If you
do not agree to these terms, you must immediately cease all use of the
Software and destroy all copies in your possession or control.

The Software is a proprietary software project developed by the BEVoid
community. This License grants you limited, revocable, non-exclusive,
non-transferable rights to use the Software strictly in accordance with
the terms set forth herein.

This is an original, independently drafted license agreement created
specifically for the BEVoid Project. It is not derived from, based on, or
adapted from any other license agreement or template.

