                   SECTION 18: STATUTE OF LIMITATIONS
================================================================================

18.1 **Limitation Period**: Any action or proceeding arising out of
     or related to this Agreement must be commenced within one (1)
     year after the cause of action accrues.

18.2 **Accrual**: A cause of action accrues when the party asserting
