18.3 **Bar**: Failure to commence an action within the limitation
     period shall constitute a perpetual bar to such action.

18.4 **Tolling**: The limitation period shall be tolled during any
     period in which Licensor is actively investigating or pursuing
     enforcement actions related to the same subject matter.

