78.1 **Obligation**: Upon termination, you shall
     destroy all copies of the Software.

78.2 **Method**: Destruction shall be by secure
     means that prevent recovery.

78.3 **Timeline**: Destruction shall occur within
     fourteen (14) days of termination.

78.4 **Certification**: You shall provide written
     certification of destruction.

78.5 **Backup**: Backup copies required by law may
     be retained subject to confidentiality
     obligations.

